01:44:04.906 --> 01:44:06.634
<i>All of a sudden. out of all
these smiling faces.</i>

1871
01:44:06.658 --> 01:44:09.244
<i>there was this one face.</i>

1872
01:44:09.286 --> 01:44:11.431
<i>I couldn't understand why I kept
looking at this one face</i>

1873
01:44:11.455 --> 01:44:14.708
<i>and then I realized why.
He wasn't smiling.</i>

1874
01:44:15.792 --> 01:44:17.586
<i>All I could see was this guy.</i>

1875
01:44:18.462 --> 01:44:20.088
<i>And nobody could see him but me.</i>

1876
01:44:24.009 --> 01:44:25.302
Come on. C.

1877
01:44:25.343 --> 01:44:29.806
-No!
-Come here!

1878
01:44:29.848 --> 01:44:31.391
(GUNSHOT)

1879
01:44:31.433 --> 01:44:34.144
(SCREAMING)

1880
01:44:36.521 --> 01:44:37.898
Get an ambulance!

1881
01:44:58.335 --> 01:45:00.796
<i>The guy that killed Sonny was
the son of the man that he</i>

1882
01:45:00.837 --> 01:45:03.757
<i>killed eight years earlier in
front of my house.</i>

1883
01:45:08.011 --> 01:45:11.723
("AVE MARIA" PLAYING)

1884
01:45:42.212 --> 01:45:45.048
<i>There were flowers all over the place.</i>

1885
01:45:45.090 --> 01:45:47.884
<i>Gangsters have this thing about flowers.</i>

1886
01:45:47.926 --> 01:45:50.929
<i>They think whoever sends the
biggest arrangement cares most.</i>

1887
01:45:53.056 --> 01:45:55.183
(SOBBING)

1888
01:46:03.900 --> 01:46:05.740
-John and Anthony from Detroit.
-How are you?

1889
01:46:10.282 --> 01:46:12.242
Did you see the way he went down.
Bum. bum. bang!

1890
01:46:15.245 --> 01:46:17.581
<i>It was just like Sonny said it would be.</i>

1891
01:46:19.291 --> 01:46:23.211
<i>Nobody cares. Nobody cares.</i>

1892
01:46:26.464 --> 01:46:29.926
(CROWD CHATTING)

1893
01:46:39.561 --> 01:46:41.813
I'm sorry. C. but we got to close up now.

1894
01:46:44.316 --> 01:46:47.235
Listen. Jerry. could you just
give me a couple more minutes?

1895
01:46:47.277 --> 01:46:48.904
OK. I'll be in my office.

1896
01:47:10.091 --> 01:47:14.054
How are you doing. Sonny.
Not so good. huh?

1897
01:47:15.805 --> 01:47:18.058
She passed the test. That's what
I wanted to tell you.

1898
01:47:19.476 --> 01:47:22.312
She might be my first great one.

1899
01:47:22.354 --> 01:47:25.690
And I'm gonna go out with her.
Thanks for helping me.

1900
01:47:27.692 --> 01:47:29.045
I wanna thank you for saving my life.

1901
01:47:29.069 --> 01:47:30.904
I never got a chance to tell you.

1902
01:47:32.572 --> 01:47:38.203
They all died. Slick. Aldo.
Mario. Ralphie. All of them.

1903
01:47:39.120 --> 01:47:40.789
(APPROACHING FOOTSTEPS)

1904
01:47:42.624 --> 01:47:45.418
Sorry. I thought I was alone.
I'm just thinking out loud.

1905
01:47:45.460 --> 01:47:47.295
That's OK. It's understandable.

1906
01:47:52.008 --> 01:47:54.970
See. this man here is a great man.
He saved my life.

1907
01:47:55.553 --> 01:47:56.888
Yeah?

1908
