-Yeah.
-Sonny told me all about you.

1911
01:48:08.191 --> 01:48:10.819
Sorry. but I don't even know
who you are.

1912
01:48:10.860 --> 01:48:13.154
My name is Carmine.

1913
01:48:13.196 --> 01:48:15.865
We go back a long way together.
Sonny and me.

1914
01:48:17.826 --> 01:48:19.828
He saved my life too once.

1915
01:48:24.582 --> 01:48:26.334
You don't remember me. do you?

1916
