of things for a while.
If you need anything.

1926
01:48:57.282 --> 01:49:00.785
I want you to come and see me
at the bar. OK?

1927
01:49:00.827 --> 01:49:02.972
I think I'm gonna give the bar a
rest for a while. but...

1928
01:49:02.996 --> 01:49:05.415
-thanks anyway.
-It's OK. I understand.

1929
