1930
01:49:11.379 --> 01:49:12.380
No.

1931
01:49:26.436 --> 01:49:29.272
Don't forget. You need anything.
you come to the bar and see me.

1932
01:49:30.648 --> 01:49:33.109
-Anything.
-All right.

1933
